  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Inoperable locally advanced, recurrent, and/or metastatic adenocarcinoma of the
             stomach or gastro-esophageal junction

          -  Adult patients &gt;=18 years of age

          -  Performance Status- Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group (ECOG) 0-2;

          -  At least have one measurable disease(according to RECIST)

          -  Adequate bone marrow,renal and liver function

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous chemotherapy for advanced/metastatic disease

          -  Lack of physical integrity of the upper gastrointestinal tract, or malabsorption
             syndrome
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
